lead_paragraph: South Korean veteran K.J. Choi moved within sight of his ninth PGA Tour victory when he earned a share of the lead with American Scott Brown after the third round at the Farmers Insurance Open on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Choi Seeks to End Drought in Rain at Torrey Pines
